        "content": "<p>alexcrichton created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/9477#discussion_r1803917254\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Looks good to me!</p>\n</blockquote>",
